outlierReplace = function(dataframe, cols, rows, newValue = NA) {
    if (any(rows)) {
        set(dataframe, rows, cols, newValue)
    }
}
outlierReplace(Houses_true, "Price", which(Houses_true$Price > 6000000), NA)
outlierReplace(Houses_true, "Rooms", which(Houses_true$Rooms > 8), NA)
outlierReplace(Houses_true, "Distance", which(Houses_true$Distance > 40), NA)
outlierReplace(Houses_true, "Bedroom2", which(Houses_true$Bedroom2 > 8), NA)
outlierReplace(Houses_true, "Bathroom", which(Houses_true$Bathroom > 7.5), NA)

Houses_true<- Houses_true %>% na.exclude(Houses_true)
